---
import DocsLayout from '../../layouts/DocsLayout.astro';
---

<DocsLayout title="Concepts">
  <h1 class="text-3xl font-semibold mb-6">All Reference Pages</h1>

  <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-4">
    <a href="/concepts/llm-architecture" class="block p-5 bg-slate-900 border border-slate-800 rounded-3xl hover:border-blue-600">
      <div class="font-medium">Architecture &amp; the Predictor Seam</div>
      <div class="text-sm text-slate-400">The narrow waist and layered design.</div>
    </a>

    <a href="/concepts/llm-readme" class="block p-5 bg-slate-900 border border-slate-800 rounded-3xl hover:border-blue-600">
      <div class="font-medium">LLM Prototypes Guide</div>
      <div class="text-sm text-slate-400">Living reference for every prototype + sequencing.</div>
    </a>

    <a href="/concepts/prototype-roadmap" class="block p-5 bg-slate-900 border border-slate-800 rounded-3xl hover:border-blue-600">
      <div class="font-medium">The 9-Prototype Roadmap</div>
      <div class="text-sm text-slate-400">Rationale, production mirrors, and status.</div>
    </a>

    <a href="/concepts/sampling-strategies" class="block p-5 bg-slate-900 border border-slate-800 rounded-3xl hover:border-blue-600">
      <div class="font-medium">Sampling Strategies</div>
      <div class="text-sm text-slate-400">Top-k, Top-p, and why temperature alone is not enough.</div>
    </a>
  </div>

  <div class="mt-8 text-sm text-slate-400">
    These pages are rendered from the project's canonical Markdown sources.
    The single-file <a href="/knowledge-reflection-tester.html" class="underline">Knowledge Tester</a> provides active recall over the same concepts.
  </div>
</DocsLayout>